snippet.textDisplay:
So beautiful, Keep rocking Anuv Jain. "Arz Kiya Hai" on Coke Studio Bharat is a mesmerizing blend of his signature indie-pop style with a fresh, raw energy. The song beautifully captures the innocence and heartache of young love, with Jain's soulful vocals conveying a deep sense of longing. It’s a track that feels both intimate and universal, leaving a lasting impression with its simple lyrics yet powerful emotional honesty.
🇵🇰💚🇮🇳
